        <updateDate>2021-02-23T18:24:59Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Emergency Grants of Release And Compassion Effectively Act of 2020 or the Emergency GRACE Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes various changes to address COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) and expand the use of compassionate release programs in correctional facilities, including by providing emergency funding to nonfederal correctional facilities.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
